# Sample client certificates and keys

Replace ca.crt with your own client certificate authority to verify and sign client certificates. 
May be you already using one for your organization, then just copy the ca.crt in this directory.

### user.pfx is a sample client certificate that will authenticate you if you install it in your browser
with sample ca.crt.

# IMPORTANT

Do not leave the sample ca.crt in this directory, replace it with your own!

There are pleanty of instructions how ssl client certificate authentication works. Here is just one of them:
* https://www.makethenmakeinstall.com/2014/05/ssl-client-authentication-step-by-step/
